entry.string:
if ! [ -x "$(command -v docker-compose)" ]; then echo "Installing Docker Compose..." curl -L "https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.29.2/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m)" -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose else echo "Docker Compose is already installed." fi
docker --version docker-compose --version
